<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to <%= site_name %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      border: 1px solid #000a185d;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #000a18;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #d85600;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="<%= site_name %>" class="logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= user.full_name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for signing up! ðŸŽ‰ We're thrilled to have you as part of the <%= site_name %> community.</p>

      <p>Hereâ€™s what you can do next:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Explore our platform and discover what we offer.</li>
        <li>Complete your profile to get the best experience.</li>
        <li>Start using your dashboard to access our services.</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="<%= web_url %>/user/dashboard" class="btn">Go to Dashboard</a>

      <p>If you have any questions or need support, feel free to contact us anytime.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= site_name %>. All rights reserved. <br />
      Need help? Contact us at <%= contact_email %>.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
